                      </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-3 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg">
                      <h5 class="font-medium text-green-800">Φ150×300 mm hengerek</h5>
                      <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                        <li>• Nemzetközi standardokhoz</li>
